result.name: Ka Ho Restaurant

reviews.text: The traditional Chinese restaurant inside the public housing, where is easy to wait for seat comparative at Telford shopping ctr and Amoy plaza.
Nice dim sum
晚市一間很大的酒樓， 但人流不多 非常淡静！ 菜式一般不過不失， 街坊都不妨幫襯下。
區內兢爭甚大，經營各具特色，嘉豪算是區內最豪裝的酒樓，價錢克制，服務都達水準，值得捧場。
坐位舒適，但服務一般，食物質素平庸冇驚喜！但價錢不平與食物不成比例，不光顧冇損失！！

reviews.text: Small plaza but cute and good shop.
For shopping centre ....so good place
The shopping mall contains a supermarket, a post office, multiple restaurants, and stores. It also has a carpark which offers parking spaces at relatively low rent.
Not for those who wants to get luxury products, only for those who wants need to purchase necessities.
very bad environment shopping mall.The mall is such dark and old.But the restruant inside the mall are well and tasty.
